  "detailed_description": "Are you ready to find the difference? Then quickly run after the magnifying glass and get ready to spot the differences in an exciting puzzle game!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540690/extras/a914c19fca19520bc391653608d8b701.avif?t=1692643818\" width=616 height=242 /></span><br>Your goal is to mark the differences in the picture by clicking on each of them. Each level features two cute, hand-drawn pictures.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540690/extras/e6dca77585cc98d5af2a8d5cf8ebf112.avif?t=1692643818\" width=616 height=240 /></span><br>There are 10 levels in total, for the flawless passage of each of which you will receive an achievement!",
